        <mxCell id="note" value="Transition notes&#xa;- Activate, assign, check in, check out, clean, inspect, pass inspection.&#xa;- Issue reporting can send a room to Maintenance or Out of Service.&#xa;- Maintenance can resolve to Dirty, Inspection Required, or Available.&#xa;- Deactivate moves a room to Inactive; Inactive can reactivate or retire." style="rounded=0;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fontSize=11;fillColor=#f5f5f5;strokeColor=#999999;align=left;spacing=8;" vertex="1" parent="1"><mxGeometry x="1240" y="310" width="310" height="190" as="geometry"/></mxCell>
